snippet.title: Character Demo - "Clorinde: Night Vigil Amidst Candlelit Shadows" | Genshin Impact #Clorinde
snippet.description:
There are many things to watch out for while traveling in the dead of the night.
Traps under our feet, beasts lurking in the shadows, surprise attacks from the air or behind our backs...
But the greatest danger is the fear that lies deep within one's heart.
